snippet.title: Pushpa 2 The Rule Teaser | Allu Arjun | Sukumar | Rashmika Mandanna | Fahadh Faasil | DSP
snippet.description:
Pushpa 2 The Rule Teaser on Mythri Movie Makers. 

Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Written and Directed by Sukumar. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y. Ravi Shankar of Mythri Movie Makers in association with Sukumar Writings,  the film stars Allu Arjun, Fahadh Faasil, Rashmika Mandanna, Dhanunjay, Rao Ramesh, Sunil, Anasuya Bharadwaj & Ajay Ghosh. The film's music is composed by Devi Sri Prasad.

Wishing our Pushpa Raj aka Icon stAAr Allu Arjun a very Happy Birthday 🥳 #HappyBirthdayAlluArjun

snippet.title: “Modi is 80% a Dictator and a Darpok”; I Call on Indian Voters to Throw Him Out
snippet.description:
Dhruv Rathee, who is arguably the most widely followed and most highly admired YouTube video-maker of his generation in India, whose last two videos on dictatorship have together achieved nearly 50 million views, has said that Narendra Modi is “70-80% a dictator”, adding that like all ‘tanashahs’ he is “a darpok”, insecure and lacking in confidence. He’s called upon the Indian people to throw out the Modi government.

 

In a special interview to talk about himself, his childhood and upbringing, his training as a mechanical engineer at the Karlsruhe Institute of Technology, his marriage to his wife Juli and also what motivates him to make videos and the extent of preparation and effort put into each of them but also to talk about political issues such as his view of Narendra Modi as a dictator and whether India is becoming a dictatorship and his confidence in the Indian people who he has exhorted to throw the Modi government out, Dhruv Rathee said that his message to the Indian people is brief and simple: “Vote Karne Jayen to Sarkar ko nikal phenke”.

 

Dhruv Rathee says that he has faith that his 2.5 crore audience will heed his request for each person to share his video with another 100 people who, in turn, will respond to his message to vote out the Modi government.

 

I will deliberately stop there and leave you to hear Dhruv Rathee in his own language and in his inimitable style.

 

This interview consists of two large subjects i.e. personal questions about him, his life and his work and also political questions about Modi, the Opposition, the behavoiur of Governors, the Election Commission, the Enforcement Directorate and CBI as well as the Indian media and surveys that suggest that 75% of the Indian people like and admire Narendra Modi. A substantial part of the interview is about Dhruv Rathee’s confidence in his audience, viewers and fans who he believes will respond to his appeal to vote against the Modi government.

 

Right at the end, there are a few further personal questions where Dhruv Rathi says that he is very conscious of what he says to his audience and how he says it, that as of now he has no intention of joining politics but cannot speak of what happens 20 or 30 years ahead and that he’s not drawn to normal Bollywood films but could be attracted to take part in art cinema.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy:

On being refused by their parents for money, Tapu Sena starts selling their toys and other belongings to collect money. All the parents arrive at Gada's house to complain to Jethalal about Tapu being responsible for all the children's behavior.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 727
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Team Leader || Episode - 2 || Shravan Kotha || Tanmayee Bommena || Telugu Web Series 2024
snippet.description:
In a corporate setting, a group of rejected candidates from rural backgrounds faces discrimination but gets a second chance when designated to a disliked employee, Shravan, as their new team leader, causing tension and challenges in the workplace.

Cast: Shravan Kotha, Naga Tanmayee Bommena, Shrija Reddy, J. Sai Praneeth, Chenchu ​​Rakesh, Mohd Noorjahan, Thodeti Lavan Kumar, Rajender Reddy, Venkatesh Tirumani, Gurrala Madhan Mohan Reddy, Vamshi Revalla, Kumar Raja Macha, Suresh, Santhosh, Prem, Siri Latha, Adapa Lahari, Kadari Nagarani

Produced by Vandana Bandaru

Written and Directed by Shravan Kotha 

Cinematography: Bhanu Prakash Musumuri 

Editing: Vamshi, Venkat, Santosh Kumar.

Co-Director: Rahul Kambampata

Final mixing and Di : Madhu kallepalli 

Poster Designer: Nikhil Chotu

Assistant Director: Kumar Raja Macha

Assistant Dop's: Nikshay Shetty, Bhavani Prasad. 

Line Producer: Siva Gaddam, Sajeev. 

Executive Producer: Shrija Reddy

#TeamLeaderWebSeries #ShravanKotha #Tanmayee #TeluguWebSeries2024

Here is Full Video Song Of Powerful Hanuman Chalisa From HanuMan Telugu Movie, Sung By Saicharan, Music By GowraHari, Let the resonating chants of devotion fill your heart with strength and Devotion.

Stay updated with the latest videos from Tips Telugu, Subscribe on the below link
https://youtube.com/TipsTelugu

Song Details : 
Song : Hanuman Chalisa
Singer : Saicharan 
Lyrics : Traditional 
Music Director :GowraHari

Movie Details : 
Written & Directed by Prasanth Varma
Starring Teja Sajja, Amritha Aiyer, Varalakshmi Sarath Kumar, Vinay Rai, Raj Deepak Shetty, Vennela Kishore, Getup Srinu, Satya etc.,
Produced by K. Niranjan Reddy

#hanumanchalisa  #hanuman  #latesttelugumovies #telugusongs #tipstelugu #telugunewsongs #prasanthvarma #saicharan 

Lyrics: 

జయ హనుమాన జ్ఞాన గుణ సాగర
జయ కపీశ తిహు లోక ఉజాగర 

రామదూత అతులిత బలధామా
అంజని పుత్ర పవనసుత నామా 

మహావీర విక్రమ బజరంగీ
కుమతి నివార సుమతి కే సంగీ

కంచన వరణ విరాజ సువేశా
కానన కుండల కుంచిత కేశా 

హాథవజ్ర ఔ ధ్వజా విరాజై 
కాంథే మూంజ జనేవూ సాజై 

శంకర సువన కేసరీ నందన 

విద్యావాన గుణీ అతి చాతుర 
రామ కాజ కరివే కో ఆతుర 

ప్రభు చరిత్ర సునివే కో రసియా 
రామలఖన సీతా మన బసియా

సూక్ష్మ రూపధరి సియహి దిఖావా 
వికట రూపధరి లంక జలావా 

భీమ రూపధరి అసుర సంహారే 
రామచంద్ర కే కాజ సంవారే

లాయ సంజీవన లఖన జియాయే 
శ్రీ రఘువీర హరషి ఉరలాయే

రఘుపతి కీన్హీ బహుత బడాయీ 
తుమ మమ ప్రియ భరత సమ భాయీ 

సహస్ర వదన తుమ్హరో యశగావై 
అస కహి శ్రీపతి కంఠ లగావై 


సనకాదిక బ్రహ్మాది మునీశా 
నారద శారద సహిత అహీశా 

యమ కుబేర దిగపాల జహాం తే 
కవి కోవిద కహి సకే కహాం తే 

తుమ ఉపకార సుగ్రీవహి కీన్హా 
రామ మిలాయ రాజపద దీన్హా 

తుమ్హరో మంత్ర విభీషణ మానా 
లంకేశ్వర భయే సబ జగ జానా 

యుగ సహస్ర యోజన పర భానూ 
లీల్యో తాహి మధుర ఫల జానూ 

ప్రభు ముద్రికా మేలి ముఖ మాహీ
జలధి లాంఘి గయే అచరజ నాహీ 

దుర్గమ కాజ జగత కే జేతే 
సుగమ అనుగ్రహ తుమ్హరే తేతే 

రామ దుఆరే తుమ రఖవారే 
హోత న ఆజ్ఞా బిను పైసారే 

సబ సుఖ లహై తుమ్హారీ శరణా 
తుమ రక్షక కాహూ కో డర నా 

ఆపన తేజ సమ్హారో ఆపై 
తీనోం లోక హాంక తే కాంపై 

భూత పిశాచ నికట నహి ఆవై 
మహవీర జబ నామ సునావై 

నాసై రోగ హరై సబ పీరా 
జపత నిరంతర హనుమత వీరా

సంకట సే హనుమాన ఛుడావై 
మన క్రమ వచన ధ్యాన జో లావై 

సబ పర రామ తపస్వీ రాజా 
తినకే కాజ సకల తుమ సాజా 

ఔర మనోరథ జో కోయి లావై 
తాసు అమిత జీవన ఫల పావై 

చారో యుగ ప్రతాప తుమ్హారా
హై ప్రసిద్ధ జగత ఉజియారా 

సాధు సంత కే తుమ రఖవారే 
అసుర నికందన రామ దులారే

అష్ఠసిద్ధి నవ నిధి కే దాతా
అస వర దీన్హ జానకీ మాతా 

రామ రసాయన తుమ్హారే పాసా 
సదా రహో రఘుపతి కే దాసా 

తుమ్హరే భజన రామకో పావై 
జన్మ జన్మ కే దుఖ బిసరావై 

అంత కాల రఘుపతి పురజాయీ 
జహాం జన్మ హరిభక్త కహాయీ 

ఔర దేవతా చిత్త న ధరయీ 
హనుమత సేయి సర్వ సుఖ కరయీ 

సంకట క(హ)టై మిటై సబ పీరా 
జో సుమిరై హనుమత బల వీరా 

జై జై జై హనుమాన గోసాయీ 
కృపా కరహు గురుదేవ కీ నాయీ 

జో శత వార పాఠ కర కోయీ 
ఛూటహి బంది మహా సుఖ హోయీ 

జో యహ పడై హనుమాన చాలీసా 
హోయ సిద్ధి సాఖీ గౌరీశా 

తులసీదాస సదా హరి చేరా 
కీజై నాథ హృదయ మహ డేరా

భీమ రూపధరి అసుర సంహారే 
రామచంద్ర కే కాజ సంవారే

లాయ సంజీవన లఖన జియాయే 
శ్రీ రఘువీర హరషి ఉరలాయే

రఘుపతి కీన్హీ బహుత బడాయీ 
తుమ మమ ప్రియ భరత సమ భాయీ 

సహస్ర వదన తుమ్హరో యశగావై 
అస కహి శ్రీపతి కంఠ లగావై 


సనకాదిక బ్రహ్మాది మునీశా 
నారద శారద సహిత అహీశా 

యమ కుబేర దిగపాల జహాం తే 
కవి కోవిద కహి సకే కహాం తే 

తుమ ఉపకార సుగ్రీవహి కీన్హా 
రామ మిలాయ రాజపద దీన్హా 

తుమ్హరో మంత్ర విభీషణ మానా 
లంకేశ్వర భయే సబ జగ జానా 

యుగ సహస్ర యోజన పర భానూ 
లీల్యో తాహి మధుర ఫల జానూ 

ప్రభు ముద్రికా మేలి ముఖ మాహీ
జలధి లాంఘి గయే అచరజ నాహీ 

దుర్గమ కాజ జగత కే జేతే 
సుగమ అనుగ్రహ తుమ్హరే తేతే 

రామ దుఆరే తుమ రఖవారే 
హోత న ఆజ్ఞా బిను పైసారే 

సబ సుఖ లహై తుమ్హారీ శరణా 
తుమ రక్షక కాహూ కో డర నా 

ఆపన తేజ సమ్హారో ఆపై 
తీనోం లోక హాంక తే కాంపై 

భూత పిశాచ నికట నహి ఆవై 
మహవీర జబ నామ సునావై 

నాసై రోగ హరై సబ పీరా 
జపత నిరంతర హనుమత వీరా

సంకట సే హనుమాన ఛుడావై 
మన క్రమ వచన ధ్యాన జో లావై 

సబ పర రామ తపస్వీ రాజా 
తినకే కాజ సకల తుమ సాజా 

ఔర మనోరథ జో కోయి లావై 
తాసు అమిత జీవన ఫల పావై 

చారో యుగ ప్రతాప తుమ్హారా
హై ప్రసిద్ధ జగత ఉజియారా 

సాధు సంత కే తుమ రఖవారే 
అసుర నికందన రామ దులారే

అష్ఠసిద్ధి నవ నిధి కే దాతా
అస వర దీన్హ జానకీ మాతా 

రామ రసాయన తుమ్హారే పాసా 
సదా రహో రఘుపతి కే దాసా 

తుమ్హరే భజన రామకో పావై 
జన్మ జన్మ కే దుఖ బిసరావై 

అంత కాల రఘుపతి పురజాయీ 
జహాం జన్మ హరిభక్త కహాయీ 

ఔర దేవతా చిత్త న ధరయీ 
హనుమత సేయి సర్వ సుఖ కరయీ 

సంకట క(హ)టై మిటై సబ పీరా 
జో సుమిరై హనుమత బల వీరా 

జై జై జై హనుమాన గోసాయీ 
కృపా కరహు గురుదేవ కీ నాయీ 

జో శత వార పాఠ కర కోయీ 
ఛూటహి బంది మహా సుఖ హోయీ 

జో యహ పడై హనుమాన చాలీసా 
హోయ సిద్ధి సాఖీ గౌరీశా 

తులసీదాస సదా హరి చేరా 
కీజై నాథ హృదయ మహ డేరా

सैंये खैतों फुल्ल फूलल रोटी जोगल हमर कोठी के

सैंया जब टानते जैयतो रे छाती तोर फाटते जैयतों रे

snippet.title: സൂര്യഗ്രഹണം - സത്യവും മിഥ്യയും | Solar Eclipse April 8 2024 | Solar Eclipse Explained Malayalam
snippet.description:
The world is going to witness a total solar eclipse on April 8 2024. Solar eclipses are rare events for humans. One in every ten thousand people can see a total solar eclipse in their lifetime. This video explains the science behind the event of solar eclipse and why solar eclipses are very rare in nature. The inclination of the moon's orbital plane, the occurrence of lunar nodes, and the alignment of the sun, the moon and the earth in a straight line which leads to the moon's shadow on earth which causes the solar eclipse are explained in this video. There are many myths surrounding solar eclipses like you cannot go out or eat food during a solar eclipse. This video explains why the myths surrounding the solar eclipse are false. This video is a must watch before the solar eclipse 2024 on April 8th.

#solareclipse2024 #totalsolareclipse #alexplain

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

What happens when a girl who is unable to get married, is sought after by a family of repute happily accepted the girl as the daughter in law. Seeing their ideology on promoting women empowerment, the girl is hopeful that she will fulfil her ambition of learning to speak English but she discovers that the family she is married into has ulterior motives. Watch this powerful serial SUNAYANA @7.30PM - Only on Sidharth TV

snippet.title: Solar Eclipse 2024: இன்று நிகழப்போகும் சூரிய கிரகணம் ஏன் நூற்றாண்டின் அரிய நிகழ்வு? Nasa Plan என்ன?
snippet.description:
ஏப்ரல் 8 ஆம் தேதி சூரிய கிரகணத்தைக் காண உலகெங்கிலும் உள்ள மக்கள் ஆர்வமாக உள்ளனர். வட அமெரிக்காவின் சில பகுதிகளில் இந்த முழு சூரிய கிரகணத்தைக் காண முடியும். இந்த சூரிய கிரகணத்தின் போது, நான்கு நிமிடங்கள் மற்றும் ஒன்பது வினாடிகளுக்கு முழு இருள் இருக்கும்.

#SolarEclipse #Moon #Sun

snippet.title: Hotstar Specials Taaza Khabar Season 2 | Coming Soon | @hotstarOfficial
snippet.description:
Zindagi badi ajeeb hai...
#hotstarspecials  #TaazaKhabar Season 2 coming soon only on @hotstarOfficial 

Watch #HotstarSpecials Taaza Khabar only on Disney+ Hotstar: http://www.hotstar.com/1260127221

#TaazaKhabarOnHotstar #BhuvanBam #ShriyaPilgaonkar @BBKVProductions

--

With good Karma on one’s side, can one man set out to become a master of his own destiny? 

Disney+ Hotstar’s upcoming fantasy-drama series, Hotstar Specials presents Taaza Khabar explores just this with the one of India’s most beloved content creator, Bhuvan Bam in the lead. Set in Mumbai, this one-of-a-kind uplifting series will take viewers on a riveting ride of a man stumbling upon a miracle and the ripples it creates in his humble life. 

The series is being directed by Himank Gaur  produced by Rohit Raj under the banner of BB Ki Vines Productions. The show has been penned by powerful writer duo Hussain Dalal & Abbas Dalal and also stars Shriya Pilgaonkar, Mahesh Manjrekar, Deven Bhojani, Prathmesh Parab and Nitya Mathur in pivotal roles.
 
The resounding success of Taaza Khabhar season 1 is a testament to Disney+ Hotstar’s commitment in its pursuit of bringing quality entertainment. The heartfelt response and immense love "Taaza Khabar" received from you all have been overwhelming. It's been a testament to the power of storytelling, the dedication of our talented cast who brought this unique tale to life. The success of the first season was marked by it being the 3rd most watched show on OTT with over 30 million viewers!

Our team is reuniting to delve deeper into the extraordinary world we've created, promising to bring you a season that's as enchanting and engaging as the first. This journey, from the inception of the first season to the anticipation of the next, has been incredible, and it's all thanks to your support and love.

Instagram► https://www.instagram.com/bhuvan.bam22/           
Facebook► https://www.facebook.com/BBkiVines/
Twitter►https://twitter.com/Bhuvan_Bam

Follow  @BBKVProductions   for BTS & more updates.

#TaazaKhabarOnHotstar #BBKiVinesProductions #BhuvanBam

Bhuvan Bam is a comedian, singer-songwriter, actor and entrepreneur. He created the entire universe of BB Ki Vines, a content power house, to see more of his content follow him on

snippet.title: ঈদের চাঁদ নিয়ে মুসলিম দেশগুলোয় যে কারণে এত বির্তক । BBC Bangla
snippet.description:
অনেক দেশ সৌদি আরবের সাথে মিলিয়ে ঈদ পালন করলেও বিশ্বের অনেক দেশে এর আগে কিংবা পরে ঈদ উদযাপন করা হয়। ঈদের চাঁদ নিয়ে মুসলিম দেশগুলোতে এত বিতর্কের কারণ কী?

#ঈদ #চাঁদ #ঈদের_চাঁদ #ঈদুলফিতর #eid #eidulfitr #moon 
*******************************************
বিবিসি নিউজ বাংলার ইউটিউব চ্যানেলে আপনাকে স্বাগতম। 
এখানে আপনি দেখতে পাবেন দেশ ও দেশের বাইরের সমসাময়িক গুরুত্বপূর্ণ ঘটনাবলী নিয়ে বস্তুনিষ্ঠ ও বিশ্লেষণধর্মী প্রতিবেদন, বিবিসি নিউজ বাংলার টিভি অনুষ্ঠান প্রবাহ এবং বাংলাদেশ ট্রেন্ডিং-এর সকল পর্ব।  নিয়মিত ভিডিও আপডেট পেতে এবং অনুষ্ঠান দেখতে সাবস্ক্রাইব করতে ভুলবেন না!

আমাদের সঙ্গে যুক্ত হতে পারেন:
ওয়েবসাইট: bbcbangla.com
ফেসবুক: https://www.facebook.com/BBCBengaliService/

snippet.title: Navratri Special Song | Maa Sherawali | Navratri Mata Bhajan 2024 | Shekhar Jaiswal
snippet.description:
Shekhar Jaiswal Presents Navratri Special Mata Bhajan Mere Ghar Aao Maa Sherowali

Shekhar Jaiswal Instagram - 

Audio & Video :-
Song - Maa Sherowali
Singer Composer Lyrics - Shekhar Jaiswal
Music - GW Music Studio Rudrapur
Cinematography - Lucky Hundal
Director - Soumya Jaiswal
Cast - Laxmi Devi, Shekhar Jaiswal, Soumya Jaiswal, Vinod
Location - Surajmal Dunga Mandir Kiccha & Lalkuan Uttarakhand
Editing - Shekhar Jaiswal
Manage By - YT Media Entertainment

For Shows & Collabs - 9719998366, 7451940400
Shekharredifmail@gmail.com

Lyrics -
------------------------------
Tere dar ki hai shan nirali..x2
Mere ghar aao maa sherowali..x2

Darshn de upkar tu karde
Khali pade bhandar tu bharde..x2
Apne bhakto kar rakhwali
Tuhi durga tuhi mahakali
Tere dar ki shan nilari
Mere ghar aao maa sherowali

Hey jag ki janni Maiya Meri
Ambe dukh harni Maiya Meri
Tu bigdi bana de
Bhav Par laga de maiya hai
Kya lage mera Maiya Meri
Sb kuch hai tera Maiya Meri
Tu Kasht mita de 
Mere Bhagy jaga de Maiya Meri
Me balak tera Maiya Meri
Kya laage mera Maiya Meri
Tuhi h data 
Tuhi Bagya vidhata Maiya Meri
Maa Jholiya bharde Maiya Meri
Beghar ko gharde Maiya Meri
Shakhar ki sunle
Sare dukh harle 
Tere dar se na jaunga khali
Tuhi data hai hum hai bhikhari
Tere dar ki shan nirali...
Mere ghar aao maa sherowali...x4

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.description:

Khumar Episode 41 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 5th April 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem
Hina Bayat as Kehkasha Begum
Asma Abbas as Durdana
Behroz Sabzwari as Sheikh Furqan
Zainab Qayoom as Dil Araa
Shehryar Zaidi as Taufeeq
Adnan Samad as Nasir
Sheherzade Peerzada as Hamna  
Minsa Malik as Laiba 
Kinza Malik as Atiya

snippet.title: चैत्र अमावस्या सोमवार : आज सोमवती अमावस्या की चमत्कारी कथा को सुनने से सभी कष्ट, संकट दूर होते है
snippet.description:
Chaitra Somvati Amavasya :
सोमवार 8 अप्रैल को चैत्र मास की अमावस्या है. सोमवार को अमावस्या होने से इसे सोमवती अमावस्या कहा जाता है. इस दिन व्रत, कथा, पूजन और पवित्र नदियों में स्नान का भी विशेष महत्व है. महिलाएं सोमवती अमावस्या के दिन पति की लंबी आयु के लिए व्रत रखती हैं. पितृ दोष निवारण के लिए दिन अत्यंत शुभ माना गया है गरुड़ पुराण में बताया गया है कि सोमवती अमावस्या के दिन पितरों को तर्पण करने से पितृ दोष से मुक्ति मिलती है इस अमावस्या में किए गए दान-पुण्य और तीर्थ स्नान से अक्षय पुण्य मिलता है.

सोमवती अमावस्या समय :
8 अप्रैल को तड़के 3.21 बजे शुरू
8 अप्रैल को ही रात 11.50 बजे समाप्त

Chaitra Somvati Amavasya :
सोमवार 8 अप्रैल को चैत्र मास की अमावस्या है. सोमवार को अमावस्या होने से इसे सोमवती अमावस्या कहा जाता है. इस दिन व्रत, कथा, पूजन और पवित्र नदियों में स्नान का भी विशेष महत्व है. महिलाएं सोमवती अमावस्या के दिन पति की लंबी आयु के लिए व्रत रखती हैं. पितृ दोष निवारण के लिए दिन अत्यंत शुभ माना गया है गरुड़ पुराण में बताया गया है कि सोमवती अमावस्या के दिन पितरों को तर्पण करने से पितृ दोष से मुक्ति मिलती है इस अमावस्या में किए गए दान-पुण्य और तीर्थ स्नान से अक्षय पुण्य मिलता है.

सोमवती अमावस्या समय :
8 अप्रैल को तड़के 3.21 बजे शुरू
8 अप्रैल को ही रात 11.50 बजे समाप्त
